{"tid":1738064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教育界聲援poly 手足 SOS","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:59:58.000Z","uid":270455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41fbde995b6f8fdb0947dd01e79c50563d8ef719","tid":1738064,"uid":270455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLZPDbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLZPDbW.jpg&h=959f3bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位教育界同工請注意⚠ 我們必須站出來為教育界發聲聲援Poly入面既手足。希望大家可以企出黎，為理工入面一百個手足打氣。<br />\n<br />\n屆時我們亦有需要運送物資入內，FA物資亦有同工運送來，但請自備防具。可以的話，亦可自備少量物資，食物，水，急救品及乾淨衣物。  <br />\n<br />\n🚩首批準時出席到既老師，每人自備一個袋，用作分擔部份Fa物資。可於4:30 半島酒店集合，幫忙運送物資，屆時我們會再到有關集合地點集合。<br />\n<br />\nFA 物資主要真係 :<br />\n大量傷口處理用品<br />\n冰袋<br />\n簡單藥物<br />\n生理鹽水<br />\n<br />\n🚩6:30 集合地點容後在tg channel update!<br />\n<br />\n即時資訊請留意以下Telegram channel : <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=94c770f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\n<br />\nFb page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101323324668085/posts/107906457343105?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101323324668085%2Fposts%2F107906457343105%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=3affe72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101323324668085/posts/107906457343105?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"48212b77e70cc0d394442bcdff586a4bac6a058e","tid":1738064,"uid":114638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"推呀！救手足呀！"},{"pid":"43ac7a95d8e60480436a2e1db46c56ff762bb66f","tid":1738064,"uid":270455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"自推！人命關天！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hk